data.description: A great 4BR, 3B, 2 car garage brick home on an oversized lot in an excellent cul-de-sac location.  Many amenities throughout the home including a large living area with a beautiful rock fireplace, large dining room, granite counter tops, surround sound speakers and security system.  The primary bedroom is HUGE with walk-in closets and a large bath.  Outside features include covered patio, privacy fence, large shade trees and a very nice high quality above ground pool.
